title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 30 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 30 2022
description:
Biden backs killing filibuster to codify abortion, but Manchin and Sinema say no. Dems aren't done with covid, but you can stop them in November. Arizona AG Mark Brnovich joins Clay and Buck to talk about SCOTUS ruling for Biden on Remain in Mexico, his campaign for Senate, and breaking news that USC and UCLA are leaving the Pac-12 for the Big Ten. Dems freak over SCOTUS ruling against EPA. C&B take a call on the 2024 race. 

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
